88
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:39,083
Dia menjemput Megan di sekolah,
dan aku di Rumah Sakit...

89
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:41,891
Dia mencuri banyak tabung
oksigen dari tempat itu.

90
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,963
Lalu kami bertiga bergegas
menjemput Tara.

91
00:11:44,120 --> 00:11:47,090
Aku di kantor polisi,
sedang bekerja.

92
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:52,849
Dengan semua yang terjadi...

93
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:56,971
...serangan itu,
Militer pergi ke Atlanta...

94
00:11:57,120 --> 00:11:59,487
...dia takkan biarkan kami
lepas dari pandangannya.

95
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:00,801
Untungnya, truk pria tua itu...

96
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:03,645
...cukup banyak persediaan
dengan pasta...

97
00:12:03,800 --> 00:12:07,441
...saus kalkun, dan <i>roni stick</i> ini.

98
00:12:07,600 --> 00:12:11,605
Meg, Kakek perlu istirahat.

99
00:12:11,760 --> 00:12:14,286
- Lily.
- Tentu, Ayah.

100
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,810
Di hitungan ketiga.

101
00:12:20,960 --> 00:12:22,610
Tolong kami, Pria Besar.

102
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:26,087
Ini.

103
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,163
Benar.
Tidak, bukan kau.

104
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:30,004
Pria lain di ruangan ini.

105
00:12:30,160 --> 00:12:32,925
Tara.

106
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:35,082
Baiklah.

107
00:12:35,240 --> 00:12:36,685
Di hitungan ketiga.

108
